TI  == [actinomyces odontolyticus, first study in france].
AB  == the authors report the detailed study of a strain of actinomyces odontolyticus isolated from a pleural liquid. gas-liquid chromatography can specify the biochemistral metabolism of the germ and set off an endocellular lipidolytic activity.
